sentences: Han Seung-yeon (born July 24, 1988), better known mononymously as Seungyeon, is a South Korean singer and actress.
She is best known as the former main vocalist of the South Korean girl group Kara and for her role in Hello, My Twenties!.
Han Seung-yeon was born on July 24, 1988, in Guri, Gyeonggi, South Korea.
